<div class="markdown"><h2>Functions</h2></div>

<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>function mask_entry(λ::AbstractVector, λc::Real, depth::Real, Δlogλ::Real)
    ifelse.(abs.(λ.-λc) .&lt;= Δlogλ * λc, depth, zero(depth))
end</code></pre>
<pre class="code-output documenter-example-output" id="var-mask_entry">mask_entry (generic function with 1 method)</pre>

<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>function line(λ::AbstractVector, λc::Real, depth::Real, σ::Real)
    1.0 .- depth .* exp.(-0.5/σ^2 .* (λ.-λc).^2 )
end</code></pre>
<pre class="code-output documenter-example-output" id="var-line">line (generic function with 1 method)</pre>

<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>function calc_mask(λ::AbstractVector, λcs::AbstractVector, depths::AbstractVector, sigma_logλ::Real, v::Real)
    @assert length(λcs) == length(depths)
    n = length(λcs)
    c::Float64
    mapreduce(i-&gt;mask_entry(λ,λcs[i]*(1+v/c),depths[i],mask_Δlogλ),.+,1:n, init=zeros(length(λ)))
end</code></pre>
<pre class="code-output documenter-example-output" id="var-calc_mask">calc_mask (generic function with 1 method)</pre>

<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>function calc_spectrum(λ::AbstractVector, λcs::AbstractVector, depths::AbstractVector, sigma_logλ::Real)
    @assert length(λcs) == length(depths)
    n = length(λcs)
    mapreduce(i-&gt;line(λ,λcs[i],depths[i],λcs[i]*sigma_logλ),.*,1:n,init=ones(length(λ)))
end</code></pre>
<pre class="code-output documenter-example-output" id="var-calc_spectrum">calc_spectrum (generic function with 1 method)</pre>

<pre class='language-julia'><code class='language-julia'>function calc_ccf(v_grid, λ, flux, mask_λs,mask_depths,sigma_logλ)
    map(v-&gt; sum(flux.*calc_mask(λ,mask_λs,mask_depths,sigma_logλ,v)),
        v_grid)
end</code></pre>
<pre class="code-output documenter-example-output" id="var-calc_ccf">calc_ccf (generic function with 1 method)</pre>
